{"tid":798835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從鄧龍威事件，看97前後分別，當年彭定康出手救身陷寃獄的區永祥 ！反觀97淪陷後香港人賤過地底泥！","createTime":"2018-08-29T14:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T14:55:36.000Z","uid":116054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"187fc3778d08171364b0dc9fa168920d5c0b630c","tid":798835,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"從鄧龍威事件，看97前後分別，當年彭定康出手救身陷寃獄的區永祥 ！反觀97淪陷後香港人賤過地底泥！<br />\n<br />\n      1991年「港人領隊區永祥被指販毒遭判終身監禁」一事，區永祥同樣涉及港人被指在菲律賓販毒、同樣是審訊期間有重要證物被銷毀或失去了，亦被質疑屬不公平審訊；不同的是，當年在立法局議員和時任港督彭定康出手襄助下，區永祥及另一港人黃銓明最終於96年以案件證據不足為由獲釋放回港。<br />\n<br />\n近期新聞:<br />\n鄧龍威被指藏毒囚終身　菲律賓交出18年前入境紀錄　<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/14344/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E8%AC%9D%E5%81%89%E4%BF%8A-%E9%84%A7%E9%BE%8D%E5%A8%81-14351/%E9%84%A7%E9%BE%8D%E5%A8%81%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%AF%92%E5%9B%9A%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB-%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E4%BA%A4%E5%87%BA18%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E8%AC%9D%E5%81%89%E4%BF%8A%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F14344%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A8%2581-14351%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25B3%2593%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA18%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%2585%25A7-&d=ZLa2RPOie54rL0mnB2p4w7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=ceb9